Minionvania Prototype
GameMaker Studio 1.4

Pixel Perfect Scaling:
 Upscale the game from 300x200 to 900x600.

 Resources > Change Global Game Settings > Windows > Graphics
 Uncheck the "Interpolate colors between pixels" option.

 Room > Settings
  Width: 300
  Height: 200
  Speed : 60

 Room > Views
  Enable the use of Views
  Clear Background with Window Colour
  View 0
  Visible when room starts
  View in room: (0, 0), 300 x 200
  Port on Screen: (0, 0), 900 x 300